Titolo: Adventure in Time

Anno: 1981

Descrizione: Adventure in Time is a text adventure for the Apple II published in 1981 by Phoenix Software. An Atari 8-bit family version was released in 1983.By means of text descriptions and two word text commands, the player travels through four locations in time, attempting to find and kill Nostradamus before he assembles a world destroying weapon.

Genere: Interactive fiction

Valutazione: N/A
